HEADWORD: Melursus
<hw>Melursus</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of mammals including
the sloth bears; in some classifications not a separate genus from
<gen>Ursus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Melursus</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
